Title: Calder hank lead wool 500g
Description: Suitable for use as a caulking agent for sealing joints between lead and steel fittings, this 1/2kg hank of Calder lead wool is made of thin strands of lead. Supplied in a range of lead alloy specifications ranging from 0 to 0.5% antimony to chemical A, lead wool is available in different make-ups to suit a variety of applications.

Title: Calder 42130032 lead flashing clips (Pack of 50)
Description: Suitable for use with lead flashings, this pack of Calder clips provides a strong, secure alternative to lead wedges, putting less pressure on the surrounding joints. Ensuring a reliable hold on the flashing, these clips also allow for natural thermal expansion.

Title: Calder expansion joint wide 3mtr x 390mm
Description: Cost-effective, durable and easy to install, this Calder 3M x 390mm gutter expansion joint is ideal for use in roof designs where traditional lead-lined gutter installations are not suitable and won't fulfil the required drip provision. The joint is made up of two lead strips connected by a vulcanised double-sided EPDM synthetic rubber band.
